'''埃里克·李·尚托''' （{{lang-en|'''Eric Lee Shanteau'''}}，{{bd|1983年|10月1日|catIdx=S}}）来自[[美国|美国]][[佐治亚州|佐治亚州]]{{link-en|利尔伯恩市|Lilburn, Georgia}}，是美国的奥运[[游泳|游泳]]选手<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://auburntigers.cstv.com/sports/c-swim/mtt/shanteau_eric00.html |title=Auburn Tigers Athlete Bio: Eric Shanteau |access-date=2009-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091208055513/http://auburntigers.cstv.com/sports/c-swim/mtt/shanteau_eric00.html |archive-date=2009-12-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。现在美国[[得克萨斯州|得克萨斯州]][[奥斯汀|奥斯汀市]]生活和训练。

== 游泳生涯 ==

=== 学生时期 ===
尚托在{{link-en|Parkview高中|Parkview High School (Georgia)}}学习时，不仅是全美游泳冠军，同时获得了4.0的GPA满分<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.usaswimming.org/USASWeb/DesktopModules/BioViewManaged.aspx?personid=902aafbb-7f55-4ba1-918f-4477e1642e3b&TabId=388&Mid=597 |title=USA Swimming Athlete Bio: Eric Shanteau |accessdate=2009-08-24 |archive-date=2012-09-14 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20120914033948/http://www.usaswimming.org/USASWeb/DesktopModules/BioViewManaged.aspx?personid=902aafbb-7f55-4ba1-918f-4477e1642e3b&TabId=388&Mid=597 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他就读于[[奧本大學|奥本大学]]期间，曾11次获得全美冠军。在[[2003年夏季世界大学生运动会|2003年世界大学生运动会]]上，尚托取得了男子400米混合泳银牌。到[[2005年夏季世界大学生运动会|2005年世界大学生运动会]]时，尚托成为了首位同时赢得男子200米和400米混合泳冠军的美国人。

2004年美国奥运游泳选拔赛（[[长滩_(加利福尼亚州)|长滩]]），尚托的男子200米和400米混合泳均名列第三，200米蛙泳获第11名，都没有进入美国的奥运参赛名单。

=== 癌症和北京奥运 ===
2008年美国奥运游泳选拔赛，尚托击败了前[[世界纪录|世界纪录]]保持者[[布伦丹·汉森|汉森]]，在男子200米蛙泳中名列第二，从而取得了参加[[奥运会|奥运会]]的参赛资格<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/olympics/article4517443.ece|title=Cancer can wait, says swimmer Eric Shanteau|date=13 August 2008|publisher=Times Online|language=en|accessdate=2008-11-18}}</ref>。其实在选拔赛的一周前，尚托已被告知自己身患[[睾丸癌|睾丸癌]]，但他还是最终决定参赛。随后，他参加了2008年[[2008年夏季奥林匹克运动会|北京奥运会]]，尽管以0.13秒之差无缘决赛<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.welt.de/english-news/article2303970/Eric-Shanteau-faces-new-battle.html|title=Eric Shanteau faces new battle|date=13 August 2008|publisher=Welt Online|language=en|accessdate=2008-11-18|archive-date=2020-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200512040930/https://www.welt.de/english-news/article2303970/Eric-Shanteau-faces-new-battle.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但他游出了自己在200米蛙泳项目上的个人最好成绩。回国后，他立刻接受了手术，目前已康复<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kvue.com/news/top/stories/111308kvue_cancer_swimmer-cb.1ab8e9fd5.html|title=Olympic swimmer joins Young Adult Alliance against cancer|date=13 November 2008|publisher=KVUE-TV|language=en|accessdate=2008-11-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090820040456/http://www.kvue.com/news/top/stories/111308kvue_cancer_swimmer-cb.1ab8e9fd5.html|archivedate=2009-08-20}}</ref>。

=== 2009年 ===
在2009年全美游泳锦标赛暨世锦赛选拔赛（[[印第安纳波利斯|印第安纳波利斯]]）中，男子100米蛙泳，尚托仅次于[[马克·冈格洛夫|马克·冈格洛夫]]以59.45的成绩位居第二<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.omegatiming.com/swimming/racearchives/2009/Indy2009/C73A1_Res1Heat_104_Finals_1_Men_100_Breast.pdf |title=2009 Conoco Phillips National Championships results: Men's 100m breaststroke final |accessdate=2009-08-24 |archive-date=2009-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090710215238/http://www.omegatiming.com/swimming/racearchives/2009/Indy2009/C73A1_Res1Heat_104_Finals_1_Men_100_Breast.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>；男子200米混合泳，尚托位居[[瑞安·洛赫特|瑞安·洛赫特]]之后获得亚军，成绩为1:56.00<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.omegatiming.com/swimming/racearchives/2009/Indy2009/C73A1_Res1Heat_122_Finals_1_Men_200_Medley.pdf |title=2009 Conoco Phillips National Championships results: Men's 200m IM final |accessdate=2009-08-24 |archive-date=2009-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090806183037/http://omegatiming.com/swimming/racearchives/2009/Indy2009/C73A1_Res1Heat_122_Finals_1_Men_200_Medley.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，是当时世界第三好成绩<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.swimnetwork.com/blogs/blog/20090710/lochte_just_misses_phelps__world_record_in_200m_im-2487.html|title=Lochte Just Misses Phelps' World Record in 200m IM|date=10 July 2009|publisher=swimnetwork.com|language=|accessdate=|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090713032425/http://www.swimnetwork.com/blogs/blog/20090710/lochte_just_misses_phelps__world_record_in_200m_im-2487.html|archivedate=2009年7月13日}}</ref>；男子200米蛙泳，尚托以2:08.01获得金牌<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.omegatiming.com/swimming/racearchives/2009/Indy2009/C73A1_Res1Heat_129_Finals_1_Men_200_Breast.pdf |title=2009 Conoco Phillips National Championships results: Men's 200m breaststroke final |accessdate=2009-08-24 |archive-date=2009-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090806090910/http://www.omegatiming.com/swimming/racearchives/2009/Indy2009/C73A1_Res1Heat_129_Finals_1_Men_200_Breast.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并打破了自己在预赛中刚刚创造的全国纪录<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.swimmingworldmagazine.com/lane9/news/21670.asp?q=USA%20Swimming%20National%20Championships:%20Eric%20Shanteau%20Lowers%20American%20Record%20in%20200%20Breast%20Again|title=Eric Shanteau Lowers American Record in 200 Breast Again|date=11 July 2009|publisher=swimmingworldmagazine.com|language=|accessdate=|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120307222550/http://www.swimmingworldmagazine.com/lane9/news/21670.asp?q=USA%20Swimming%20National%20Championships%3A%20Eric%20Shanteau%20Lowers%20American%20Record%20in%20200%20Breast%20Again|archivedate=2012年3月7日}}</ref>。尚托在参加的三个个人项目上，都游出了自己的历史最好成绩，并都取得了参加[[2009年世界游泳锦标赛|2009年世界游泳锦标赛]]的资格。

